♬｢Hey Baby So Merry｣

461
00:46:41,456 --> 00:46:47,328
♬｢Hey Baby
So Merry｣

462
00:46:47,328 --> 00:46:51,132
♬｢I wanna
hold your hand｣

463
00:46:51,132 --> 00:47:04,145
♬～

464
00:47:04,145 --> 00:47:11,019
